{"tid":739948,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"由幾時開始「驕傲」取代左「自豪」呢個字？","createTime":"2018-07-12T13:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T08:32:36.000Z","uid":140831,"like":61,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a1750b7eb389bb998acc3ebc016feec8f92d7422","tid":739948,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"明明由小學開始都有教「驕傲」係貶義詞，點解宜家無論電視電台定其他媒體都用「驕傲」呢個字黎取代「自豪」既意思，將貶義詞當褒義詞黎用，到底係我錯定宜家文化水平真係低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e8acca68762e4426d8cab13d9d9fe6385d8f7f","tid":739948,"uid":143582,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"see me fly<br />\nim proud to fly up high"},{"pid":"7067ce2cec0c2bd311d3c8e4465b8162d156384a","tid":739948,"uid":179547,"like":23,"dislike":11,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"小學生要教得簡單先會二元對立分褒貶，但好多字可以活用㗎嘛，唔通你是我的驕傲可以講成你是我的自豪咩"},{"pid":"6165525049c679df915c5c7686a4164f3f794839","tid":739948,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:16:30.000Z","msg":"proud of"},{"pid":"ed6a7424ef5e5abc467c5e15e5f9acb97fa73401","tid":739948,"uid":67203,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"多得容祖兒首我的驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間中母親節就會聽到提呢首歌"},{"pid":"8bc1c31204ec39e67582004c5a798da1563a0248","tid":739948,"uid":7840,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:22:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee39c27ed3f9afe4536d7899faf6a33b14170da3","tid":739948,"uid":140831,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"7067ce2cec0c2bd311d3c8e4465b8162d156384a","tid":739948,"uid":179547,"like":23,"dislike":11,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"小學生要教得簡單先會二元對立分褒貶，但好多字可以活用㗎嘛，唔通你是我的驕傲可以講成你是我的自豪咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"咁會唔會個歌名本身就唔岩，因為驕同傲呢兩個字我點都理解唔到點樣係褒義"},{"pid":"