00Z","msg":"為你自豪"},{"pid":"42b6f8938580e0beccfbb498269dea6b6139e286","tid":739948,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"一直學係驕傲做 adjective 係貶義<br />\n做 noun 係中性<br />\n<br />\n所以「我的驕傲」無問題，「我很驕傲」就係貶義<br />\n<br />\n等睇中文專家指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5ade998e78cd133d40fb6b019228dcac1df71e","tid":739948,"uid":130320,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"拋獲"},{"pid":"ddf603bce7ea1d091c21d1d18f005c685c348081","tid":739948,"uid":13257,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"42b6f8938580e0beccfbb498269dea6b6139e286","tid":739948,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"一直學係驕傲做 adjective 係貶義<br />\n做 noun 係中性<br />\n<br />\n所以「我的驕傲」無問題，「我很驕傲」就係貶義<br />\n<br />\n等睇中文專家指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://vicsforum.blogspot.com/2014/12/blog-post_81.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvicsforum.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F12%2Fblog-post_81.html%3Fm%3D1&d=uJLkQzv8w54hPBWmsmKDI9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=f2ac519a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://vicsforum.blogspot.com/2014/12/blog-post_81.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n/英文的 proud of 及 pride，意義偏向褒義（貶義是 complacent、arrogant），但中文的「驕傲」是貶義，榮幸、光榮、榮譽、自豪等是褒義，卻都被英文 proud of 及 pride 對譯的「驕傲」排斥掉了，不論是香港的歌星容祖兒、香港特首曾蔭權和台灣前總統陳水扁，即使自覺榮幸，也都只懂得說「我的驕傲」、「香港的驕傲」和「台灣的驕傲」。/"},{"pid":"1675b06b8b4e43ccf0d1bf17bdaa86c89cb2b395","tid":739948,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7067ce2cec0c2bd311d3c8e4465b8162d156384a","tid":739948,"uid":179547,"like":23,"dislike":11,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"小學生要教得簡單先會二元對立分褒貶，但好多字可以活用㗎嘛，唔通你是我的驕傲可以講成你是我的自豪咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"岩,  屢敗屢戰 同 屢戰屢敗 都唔應該分二元, 仲有傲慢都應該可以當褒義用"},{"pid":"ce53c7f23f5b1e616652ee89b8b01dface31c419","tid":739948,"uid":27935,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:39:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b381e81158eb71eed8daafcb3b55d70864fc1c94","tid":739948,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3b9a3cf982c958c7058299917cdd12048707d62","tid":739948,"uid":179547,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee39c27ed3f9afe4536d7899faf6a33b14170da3","tid":739948,"uid":140831,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"7067ce2cec0c2bd311d3c8e4465b8162d156384a","tid":739948,"uid":179547,"like":23,"dislike":11,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"小學生要教得簡單先會二元對立分褒貶，但好多字可以活用㗎嘛，唔通你是我的驕傲可以講成你是我的自豪咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"咁會唔會個歌名本身就唔岩，因為驕同傲呢兩個字我點都理解唔到點樣係褒義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:28:40.000Z","msg":"好多字應用上唔係非褒即貶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打理性討論先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁褒同貶都可以係主觀既 但始終好多人明明想表達自豪既意思 都會用左驕傲呢個詞 因為我理解係有差別 就正如話 我好自豪 同 我好驕傲 聽出黎都已經唔同"},{"pid":"a2050a530e50c2463764a673fd48f894b7bc0080","tid":739948,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce53c7f23f5b1e616652ee89b8b01dface31c419","tid":739948,"uid":27935,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:39:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"又係既 勉強原本係點解 真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba0b39b62a6bbfa71e1511eed3d3bd62758cebb","tid":739948,"uid":123308,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  陳雲有書《中文解毒》同埋《執正中文》，入面有講到呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/213633_f159890f1397bdc6f09027d9c3afc206.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F213633_f159890f1397bdc6f09027d9c3afc206.jpeg&h=1668714d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/213047_a97222a600567ef99adff695bbec8d42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F213047_a97222a600567ef99adff695bbec8d42.jpg&h=8c5067f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文 <del>'pound'</del> 'proud' 未必只係 disapproving，但中文「驕傲」就一定係，<br />\n褒義嘅話應該用「光榮」、「榮耀」<br />\n<br />\n特別容祖兒首歌《我的驕傲》，黃偉文填詞，成首歌歌詞都係正面，講好嘢<br />\n<br />\n英文歌詞有沿用到 original track 'Proud of You' 入面嘅 'proud'，<br />\n中文歌詞方面，係有用到「光榮」，但同時亦用咗貶義嘅「驕傲」一詞<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有好多錯中文 usage 嘅 cases，就好似「被」呢個字<br />\n<br />\n如果講正面嘅嘢，「被評為」就應該寫成「獲評為」，<br />\n「被」多數用喺負面嘅嘢上面，例如「被捕」、「被殺」，<br />\n（而家呢個年代仲有埋「被自殺」）<br />\n正面應該用「獲」<br />\n<br />\n其他例子有「被選為 xyz」應該係「獲選為 xyz」<br />\n<br />\n陳雲、余光中等有唔少書都係講呢啲劣質中文／歐化中文，值得一睇再睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582af9b2fa76203760da16464c450f8f364ba555","tid":739948,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8bc1c31204ec39e67582004c5a798da1563a0248","tid":739948,"uid":7840,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:22:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先啱"},{"pid":"4d56bd87df71bc2c17126ad1e19538eba8072833","tid":739948,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:48:19.000Z","msg":"驕傲我覺得係大部分人認同<br />\n自豪係自己感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得咋 可以討論下"},{"pid":"9ba161843b01246718ef732d50970c528b7e45f5","tid":739948,"uid":133502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:49:27.000Z","msg":"我為你自豪 我為你驕傲 我為你高歌"},{"pid":"93bc03cb6701b59ddc4e1257b553b39877c40e97","tid":739948,"uid":20654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7ba0b39b62a6bbfa71e1511eed3d3bd62758cebb","ti